{"tid":1839992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎係中共對香港人嘅大陰謀","createTime":"2020-01-24T16:11:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T16:57:10.000Z","uid":185909,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ec90d350d0d203fbc42f6b67a8dcf2bce3c41404","tid":1839992,"uid":185909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/25/001038_44c23771e705bc88402adda3f2455083.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F25%2F001038_44c23771e705bc88402adda3f2455083.jpeg&h=c88785a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實睇到呢篇野之前我都已經有懷疑，無理由連大陸醫護都有full gear +殺菌filter保護，香港無。<br />\n其二，偏偏呢幾日免費任出入港珠澳大橋。<br />\n其三，高鐵完全無檢測咁。<br />\n其四，d政府官員唔普重點樣防疫宣傳不特止，仲叫人唔好病就唔使帶口罩。<br />\n其五，印象中之前中央有講過若香港人仲唔聽話，會出皇牌。<br />\n其六，個實驗室係武漢唔記得有無培養呢隻病毒，有嘅話點解偏偏得呢隻漏咗出嚟，其他又唔會漏出嚟<br />\n<br />\n利申 公院RN<br />\n中咗生死簽嘅仲要用自己大假自我隔離<br />\n仆街港共"},{"pid":"92b56f79c84e8f759d7de4842b55501bd7e1c6b2","tid":1839992,"uid":167548,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:12:50.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">亲，神灵报梦，只要每天把此信息转发给十位朋友，诵读五遍，就可以得到保佑，百毒不侵，肺炎从此远离你～<br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">斗转星移 尽在庚子<br />\n瘟疫四起 苍生何辜<br />\n武城自封 唯有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">死</span></strong>途<br />\n国之将亡 必有妖孽<br />\n冲破囚牢 自由何价</div><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">武漢起義</span></span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"878c7fa448cb1320061ebd44c960882ea580f6c4","tid":1839992,"uid":185909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T16:14:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c68202a0e55b464328f94f08